<para id="ch13mod01_ref01">Arias, Omar and Walter W. McMahon. “Dynamic Rates of Return to Education in the U.S.” <emphasis effect="italics">Economics of Education Review</emphasis>. 20, 2001. 121–138.</para><para id="eip-820">Biography.com. 2015. “Alan Turing.” Accessed April 1, 2015. http://www.biography.com/people/alan-turing-9512017.</para><para id="eip-233">Canty Media. 2015. “The World: Life Expectancy (2015) - Top 100+.” Accessed April 1, 2015. http://www.geoba.se/population.php?pc=world&amp;type=15.</para><para id="ch13mod01_ref02">Hyclak, Thomas, Geraint Johnes, and Robert Thornton. <emphasis effect="italics">Fundamentals of Labor Economics.</emphasis> Boston: Houghton Mifflin Company, 2005.</para>
